OL,3,CChildren's social care reforms to
OL,4,Cinclude rules to stop profiteering
OL,6,FSpending by local authorities on
OL,7,Flooked-after children has more than
OL,8,Fdoubled in just over a decade, from
OL,9,F#3.1 billion in 2009/10 to #7 billion
OL,10,Fin 2022/23, the Department for
OL,11,FEducation said.
OL,13,FThe biggest 15 private providers make
OL,14,Fan average of 23% profit, according to
OL,15,Fanalysis by the Local Government
OL,16,FAssociation, which said there are more
OL,17,Fthan 1,500 children in placements each
OL,18,Fcosting the equivalent of half a
OL,19,Fmillion pounds every year.
