OL,3,CChildren's social care reforms to
OL,4,Cinclude rules to stop profiteering
OL,6,FThe new measures, to be set out in
OL,7,FParliament, are aimed at empowering
OL,8,Fsocial workers and others who work
OL,9,Fwith children to take action against
OL,10,Fproviders delivering "subpar standards
OL,11,Fof care at sky-high costs to
OL,12,Fcouncils", the department said.
OL,14,FIt added that a longstanding challenge
OL,15,Fin the system is some private
OL,16,Fproviders "siphoning off money that
OL,17,Fshould be going towards vulnerable
OL,18,Fchildren, making excessive profits or
OL,19,Frunning unregistered homes that don't
OL,20,Fmeet the right standards of care".
