OL,6,FThe Government has pledged a
OL,7,F"backstop" law, which will limit the
OL,8,Fprofit providers can make ` to be
OL,9,Fbrought in if providers do not
OL,10,Fvoluntarily put an end to
OL,11,Fprofiteering, it said.
OL,13,FOfsted will be given powers to
OL,14,Finvestigate multiple homes being run
OL,15,Fby the same company, in response to
OL,16,Frecommendations made following abuse
OL,17,Funcovered at the Hesley group of
OL,18,Fchildren's homes.
