OL,3,CChildren's social care reforms to
OL,4,Cinclude rules to stop profiteering
OL,6,FLooking at the experiences of 108
OL,7,Fchildren and young adults, it found
OL,8,Fthat some of society's most vulnerable
OL,9,Fpeople had experienced "systematic and
OL,10,Fsustained" abuse and neglect over a
OL,11,Fperiod of more than three years, with
OL,12,Fthe safety net that should have
OL,13,Fprotected them proving ineffective.
OL,15,FThe Government said it wanted to start
OL,16,Fthe process of rebalancing the system
OL,17,Fin favour of early intervention and to
OL,18,Fhelp social workers keep families
OL,19,Ftogether wherever possible.
