OL,6,FThe department said a new duty will be
OL,7,Fplaced on parents to be required to
OL,8,Fget local authority consent to
OL,9,Fhomeschool their child, if there is a
OL,10,Fchild protection inquiry or plan in
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,FIt added further plans would be laid
OL,14,Fout in the coming weeks to expand
OL,15,Fearly family help, to reduce the
OL,16,Fnumber of children entering the care
OL,17,Fsystem in the first place.
