OL,3,CChildren's social care reforms to
OL,4,Cinclude rules to stop profiteering
OL,6,FChildren's Commissioner Dame Rachel de
OL,7,FSouza said children were "paying the
OL,8,Fprice of a broken social care system"
OL,9,Fand "enduring things no child should
OL,10,Fever have to".
OL,12,FShe said: "Every child deserves to
OL,13,Fgrow up safe, happy, healthy and
OL,14,Fengaged in their communities and in
OL,15,Ftheir education. With this Bill we
OL,16,Fhave an opportunity to repair how we
OL,17,Ftreat childhood in this country.
OL,19,F"Children in the social care system
OL,20,Ftoday are living week to week in limbo.
